{"tid":1849203,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[遊記]菲律賓到此一遊","createTime":"2020-01-29T02:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T06:14:37.000Z","uid":241103,"like":11,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"73254f6b600e99f55d601bd0449477fa9408602c","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"踩完去西藏之後經過一輪休養，隻腳已經好番晒，返咗幾個月工又到新年，當然要趁呢個機會去個旅行好好玩返下<br />\n<br />\n今次唔再係獨遊，而係揾埋另外三個fd一齊去菲律賓玩。點解咁多地方唔揀要揀菲律賓呢個治安好差好似好危險既地方玩命，原因無他，因有個朋友係嗰邊一個叫PG島既地方開潛水店，可以揾佢做幾日導遊，有地膽就放心好多，享受陽光與海灘<br />\n<br />\n話說我地1月28早機出發，正正係出發前一星期，嗰邊發生嗰場43年一遇嘅火山爆發，本來仲擔心今次去唔成，不過最後都順利出發。而最巧合既係我地有一日嘅行程係打算騎馬遊火山，我地心諗，如果遊緊嘅時候爆，應該就死撚咗。為安全起見，都係取消火山行程<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/znOi385.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FznOi385.jpg&h=2b9d8d3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於只係玩5日，嗰邊又熱，所以可以輕裝上陣，淨係帶咗幾套夏天衫同相機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLEijHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLEijHJ.jpg&h=a8c47e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係live寫，出文會好慢，加上菲律賓網速差，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8702acd94b860e7aead5c8e1edc56d439ef09cfa","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:47:58.000Z","msg":"第一日<br />\n<br />\n飛0750，我0515出門，同住得好近既老死一齊坐的士過機場，再同另外兩個朋友會合。啱啱落的士，其一個朋友就打比我話佢張機票個名有粒字錯咗，要去搞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4aBQaQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4aBQaQK.jpg&h=7e32b3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機票係我負責訂嘅，買之前我填完資料影過一次比佢地double check，睇黎佢好信任我，check都冇撚check<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。當然我都有責任，最後比咗200改返啱，我話同佢一人一半<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F55QVgi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF55QVgi.jpg&h=8085b4a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎咁勁，上到機艙呢啲人多空氣又唔流通嘅地方都係飛機餐都唔食，唔除口罩穩陣。登機前見有時間，一於去咗食個早餐先<br />\n<br />\n我點咗個泰式牛肉船麵。本身唔知船面係咩，問咗問收銀姐姐，原來係蛋麵，小弟見識小，今日先知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3t3vQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3t3vQU.jpg&h=0acd5515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完就去定登機閘口，等上機。等咗陣就上機了，架機幾full，啲空姐幾靚，可能帶咗口罩。其實呢排個個帶哂口罩，係街上面好似多咗好多<br />\n靚仔靚女，因為齋睇到眼，眼嗰然係靈魂之窗，五官黎講，眼真係好難差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHbAmXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHbAmXO.jpg&h=24a406a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBbHMpK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBbHMpK.jpg&h=16aba608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係機到訓咗陣，就差唔多到，而且feel到小小熱。一落機就覺得啲熱氣來襲，好想換短衫，行去入境關卡嗰陣覺得個機場有啲細，由於係機上冇填入境表，所以卡咗陣關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520EOEp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520EOEp.jpg&h=f93cce39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gtZijL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgtZijL5.jpg&h=0878a440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到黎係門口第一時唱啲錢先，菲律賓地膽朋友叫我地帶港幣黎就ok，兌換率6.4。每人換住兩千港紙先，換完就買咗張電話卡，圍返港紙85蚊。<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係，菲律賓嘅網速真係好慢，好慢，好慢，不愧為世界五大差嘅網絡。有幾慢？香港啲限速都快過佢，而且係成日冇訊號<br />\n<br />\n搞掂晒之後就出發去第一個目的地-PG島<br />\n去嗰度要先坐兩個半鐘車，再搭一個鍾船<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EA4BQ4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEA4BQ4y.jpg&h=ffa03e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PdeeCKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdeeCKT.jpg&h=d5ab32aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n途中經過加油站停咗停，去廁所，順利行鋪頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/myobEYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmyobEYs.jpg&h=853b4cfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebn7XLb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Febn7XLb.jpg&h=f3f64a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Ur4ZYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Ur4ZYz.jpg&h=0f9a74b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又車我地去買啲口罩先，去咗間藥店，每人買咗幾盒得公司名，而乜野安全標準標籤都冇嘅三層外科口罩，圍返港紙50蚊60個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WALabw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWALabw7.jpg&h=1d880e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UATOHDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUATOHDQ.jpg&h=7b5f335b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5dGice.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5dGice.jpg&h=266bc67f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就直奔碼頭，趕上咗一點幾嘅船，除咗船飛錢，每人上船同落船都要比小費<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o40p0q2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo40p0q2.jpg&h=eaff6de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jd6HM6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjd6HM6i.jpg&h=ab4ab434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OT4x9j4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOT4x9j4.jpg&h=8442ebba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於到咗PG島，咁似長洲嘅，落咗船就見到一班行李員，菲律賓朋友比錢請咗兩個幫我啲fd搬gip，跟住就返佢間店安頓下抖下，六點半再集合，帶我地去食野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b1S4f0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb1S4f0n.jpg&h=061d7df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/608i4TY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F608i4TY.jpg&h=3ca06467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbGXA0S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbGXA0S.jpg&h=4d682525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/29/103802_9f1669045d0ac6826017de2f61c3edf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F29%2F103802_9f1669045d0ac6826017de2f61c3edf4.jpg&h=4743e67b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺低啲野就出去食晏，沿途見到唔少菲律賓餐廳，菲律賓野食啲口味真係好重，最後揀咗中式炒菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/29/103502_0c6700ef482a506a220497f865cad0a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F29%2F103502_0c6700ef482a506a220497f865cad0a9.jpg&h=3078e7e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ey09r73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fey09r73.jpg&h=9401cc4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vb9Kf1v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVb9Kf1v.jpg&h=17bdf169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢邊嘅街道都係同其他東亞國家差唔多，呢啲車  幾正。食完野行咗陣就返去訓陣，夜晚地膽朋友帶咗我地食夜同睇人妖show，飲下酒咁，飲到差唔多就返去休息<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJaQV4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJaQV4f.jpg&h=182ac164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2Em2Kn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2Em2Kn.jpg&h=9908c1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vYjNYhL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvYjNYhL.jpg&h=53df9eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw8vbCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw8vbCP.jpg&h=d6abc59a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fccdb1c62ccc851de461e5285e2b014642df0260","tid":1849203,"uid":108280,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"我聽日都出發去PG島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網上唔係好多資料<br />\n想問果邊治安係咪真係好差？<br />\n同埋有冇間潛水店嘅資料睇下"},{"pid":"a11b98d78322b2cd39f97efbd0f81490ff24c889","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fccdb1c62ccc851de461e5285e2b014642df0260","tid":1849203,"uid":108280,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"我聽日都出發去PG島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網上唔係好多資料<br />\n想問果邊治安係咪真係好差？<br />\n同埋有冇間潛水店嘅資料睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:02:37.000Z","msg":"島上治安幾好 陣間返到店 影比你睇下"},{"pid":"95863db8329fb250711acad5e79b0ecf3bea0d80","tid":1849203,"uid":47041,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:02:03.000Z","msg":"菲律賓不了"},{"pid":"6715bf4ce9750b67cded7b37c73d452eda75e88f","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a11b98d78322b2cd39f97efbd0f81490ff24c889","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fccdb1c62ccc851de461e5285e2b014642df0260","tid":1849203,"uid":108280,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"我聽日都出發去PG島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網上唔係好多資料<br />\n想問果邊治安係咪真係好差？<br />\n同埋有冇間潛水店嘅資料睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:02:37.000Z","msg":"島上治安幾好 陣間返到店 影比你睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"relax divers<br />\n<br />\n5日4夜 包6個潛套餐usd186<br />\n單房價usd40一晚<br />\n學潛水OW usd420<br />\n另外機場接送來回車連船usd270"},{"pid":"5e96fa0ffba54f627315d4b3a1b3f2ac396bba2e","tid":1849203,"uid":222145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"Ching 好耐冇見，你把長髮唔見左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22de19f6d347532e5106273c5f4b41737146e262","tid":1849203,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"有冇食賓印"},{"pid":"f2fe2411b0053946037b77e58d58f4da4228f1c9","tid":1849203,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T21:39:40.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"2f20a3474240927054684400f350bd266f1e7681","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e96fa0ffba54f627315d4b3a1b3f2ac396bba2e","tid":1849203,"uid":222145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"Ching 好耐冇見，你把長髮唔見左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:10:44.000Z","msg":"係啊 剪咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5015045af622f9d6919e369738914afbdec6a1f8","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22de19f6d347532e5106273c5f4b41737146e262","tid":1849203,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"有冇食賓印"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496feb8e63997b565b052006b619e108ff5f8328","tid":1849203,"uid":34899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"個島好靚 好想去<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n菲律賓菜係麻麻地 口味太酸<br />\n除左菲律賓燒肉 同abodo定adobo之外<br />\n我都麻麻地"},{"pid":"7f3d41a4b70eb55e5bec5387f75080e545b8d05e","tid":1849203,"uid":108280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6715bf4ce9750b67cded7b37c73d452eda75e88f","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a11b98d78322b2cd39f97efbd0f81490ff24c889","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fccdb1c62ccc851de461e5285e2b014642df0260","tid":1849203,"uid":108280,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"我聽日都出發去PG島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網上唔係好多資料<br />\n想問果邊治安係咪真係好差？<br />\n同埋有冇間潛水店嘅資料睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:02:37.000Z","msg":"島上治安幾好 陣間返到店 影比你睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"relax divers<br />\n<br />\n5日4夜 包6個潛套餐usd186<br />\n單房價usd40一晚<br />\n學潛水OW usd420<br />\n另外機場接送來回車連船usd270"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:00:16.000Z","msg":"可唔可以留個tg?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a5655575d37c17015a05bfa6847a26f00a20ab","tid":1849203,"uid":43926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"下星期我會去puerto princesa潛水<br />\n有冇人去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be315587c58a14cab02e761bd950f041c3856645","tid":1849203,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"1179541d1d3f90ca4982f4bb7ddf67a9b664381f","tid":1849203,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac5e44c82d9c665b8c18b3ce19e09356c7a870c","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:38:31.000Z","msg":"第二日<br />\n<br />\n朝早起身對住個海景食個早餐，其他幾個仲訓緊。呢間店入住包早餐，差碗麵就同香港茶記一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPhv3DL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPhv3DL.jpg&h=89fb9017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完早餐我上房補下眠，大概10幾點大家都搞掂晒，就叫地膽朋友幫我地call咗架長車車我地過白沙灘，其實我都唔知架車叫咩，成架鬼馬黃巴士咁。如果你地自己黎可以叫住宿前台幫你call車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJy4xX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJy4xX.jpg&h=7ec41f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKuyj6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKuyj6o.jpg&h=1d2223f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hx1T4yP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHx1T4yP.jpg&h=e87c8231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車費1500 php 包來回，坐咗半個鐘就到，一落車就有個agent接你去玩，十足十領隊，之後我地玩咗架船拉降傘，香蕉船同一個轉轉嘅唔知乜名<br />\n<br />\n個船長有把刀係到割繩嚇我到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZZ6KoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZZ6KoM.jpg&h=f8293388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6x6dppK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6x6dppK.jpg&h=8f59fa9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qvf9Hbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvf9Hbs.jpg&h=bcc4f91e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fH4FORu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfH4FORu.jpg&h=3858467f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩完agent帶我地去個叫X-Treme嘅地方玩，個度有7種活動玩，我既揀咗五樣，分別係卡丁車，越野四驅車，充氣撞撞撞，漆彈射擊對戰，弓箭互射對戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vkUqZZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvkUqZZD.jpg&h=d1c09887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbjqZYV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbjqZYV.jpg&h=af746b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每款都唔錯，幾過癮，比漆彈射中冇護具嘅地方都幾痛，玩越野四驅就彈成身泥，其他嘅玩到成身汗，玩完攰到一個點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G5nW6Eq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG5nW6Eq.jpg&h=6a68e55d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qvf9Hcs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqvf9Hcs.jpg&h=66db9585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b9cTpqR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb9cTpqR.jpg&h=29d8ae70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxVqfKY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxVqfKY.gif&h=7584f023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就坐返車走，返到去我地太攰，就叫前台幫我地call上門按摩，正經嘅，一個鐘500 php唔洗tip，唔貴，手勢幾好，按按下瞓著咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCmtdxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCmtdxo.jpg&h=206e31fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚地膽朋友帶我地去食韓國野，呢到啲韓餐幾好食，正常過西餐，但價錢唔平。我地每樣叫啲，最正係燉雞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zo5tXYL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZo5tXYL.jpg&h=41702ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡介下呢邊酒吧嘅價錢，普通啤酒每支120 php，圍返20蚊<br />\n<br />\n由於今日體力消耗大，我地冇去酒吧，佢哋上返房，我去咗店前面嘅海灘坐靜靜地聽海浪聲，好舒服好放鬆"},{"pid":"df2bee56c937b93ad122e2a00d3d775777235769","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3d41a4b70eb55e5bec5387f75080e545b8d05e","tid":1849203,"uid":108280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6715bf4ce9750b67cded7b37c73d452eda75e88f","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a11b98d78322b2cd39f97efbd0f81490ff24c889","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:02:37.000Z","msg":"島上治安幾好 陣間返到店 影比你睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"relax divers<br />\n<br />\n5日4夜 包6個潛套餐usd186<br />\n單房價usd40一晚<br />\n學潛水OW usd420<br />\n另外機場接送來回車連船usd270"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:00:16.000Z","msg":"可唔可以留個tg?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e514f2459524558f5ee20165430fd631f4076e5","tid":1849203,"uid":108280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df2bee56c937b93ad122e2a00d3d775777235769","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3d41a4b70eb55e5bec5387f75080e545b8d05e","tid":1849203,"uid":108280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6715bf4ce9750b67cded7b37c73d452eda75e88f","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"relax divers<br />\n<br />\n5日4夜 包6個潛套餐usd186<br />\n單房價usd40一晚<br />\n學潛水OW usd420<br />\n另外機場接送來回車連船usd270"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:00:16.000Z","msg":"可唔可以留個tg?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fa6a183ecda9f9397bd6e536a6874339de268f","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"第三日<br />\n<br />\n今日照舊落去食早餐，食完收拾咗下就準備出發去租電單車揸。呢邊租綿羊仔唔洗牌，你夠膽揸就得，我地四個人租咗兩部，每部400php一日，還車要加返油，地膽朋友自己有私伙，跟我地就正式向島嘅市中心邁進。地膽打頭陣，我中間，另一個朋友殿後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQcsusW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQcsusW.jpg&h=d613bedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51s4wGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51s4wGy.jpg&h=763abba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地膽朋友話去島中心區域要快嘅要個半鐘，慢嘅三粒鐘。開頭我同另外個朋友唔熟操作，加上後面各坐一個，所以揸得好慢，頭半個鐘都係純粹練車。<br />\n<br />\n我哋揸揸下發現最尾架車突然間跟住上，殿後個friend WhatsApp我地話撞咗，聽到個下個心離一離，佢炒咗埋牆，隻腳損咗，架車hi花左少少。 不過佢話冇問題可以繼續揸，咁我哋就繼續出發。但原本坐佢後座嘅朋友就改坐係地膽朋友嘅後座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVt7utP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVt7utP.jpg&h=ebf33ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去咗一個都幾出名嘅景點，係一個流水瀑布<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/om3fDnw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fom3fDnw.jpg&h=b89be8cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kwNcFAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkwNcFAX.jpg&h=9d3666c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家對自己手車冇乜信心真係唔好揸，基本上有八成嘅路都係上山落山嘅彎路，同埋條路比較窄，控制唔好或者唔留神嘅隨時會炒落山 <br />\n<br />\n揸咗大概兩個鐘有多先到 ，其中有啲大直路呢，都可以加速度去90公里每小時嘅，個速度感都唔錯。到咗我哋第一時間食飯先，去咗當地比較出名嘅餐廳Max's食，啲野正正常常，係我嗌嗰個咖哩伏伏地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARVxFKN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARVxFKN.gif&h=eddfd795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rJOYvx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rJOYvx.jpg&h=67e4bc23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLhoNpY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLhoNpY.jpg&h=ce0e9e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHTSFK1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvHTSFK1.jpg&h=f8b86d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我哋就一邊遊市區一邊搵口罩 ，搵咗好多間都係得啲冇標籤口罩，睇嚟呢邊啲口罩真係冇咩標準可言，見時間差唔多我哋又揸返過零兩個鐘車返去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLDGy6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLDGy6q.jpg&h=637d292a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3unix9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3unix9.jpg&h=5e8e449c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJCHiyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJCHiyf.jpg&h=0862bb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJ61y6F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJ61y6F.jpg&h=3f5f42a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸返去呢就無驚無險嘅 但由於架車撞花咗所以交車嘅時候要賠少少錢 揸成日車真係幾攰，即刻沖返個涼，準備出去食晚餐，我哋揀咗間食海鮮bbq嘅，味道都可以呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teCgn0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteCgn0v.jpg&h=00936b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完飯我地就買咗啲酒返去玩啤牌"},{"pid":"4b29b5263b2897981ad390ace9e5c3f44f1446ed","tid":1849203,"uid":241103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"第四日<br />\n<br />\n朝早食完早餐我地拎咗積咗幾日嘅衫去洗衣店洗，之後食埋晏就包咗架車車我地去玩zipline同實彈射擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mmaaLba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmaaLba.jpg&h=efb9763c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozUSd4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FozUSd4x.jpg&h=9ebcbc6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ojR5y4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojR5y4y.jpg&h=f8b8a585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去嘅途中我哋經過藥店，佢門口已經貼出口罩賣哂嘅紙，我哋心諗呢邊都一罩難求了，儘管嗰啲低防護口罩，但有戴好過冇戴，呢個原本冇人戴口罩嘅島，亦慢慢越嚟越多人戴口罩<br />\n<br />\nzipline個地方幾遠，坐車有啲耐，去到風景幾靚，但係個zipline冇預期咁長咁刺激，有啲慢 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xu835eU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxu835eU.jpg&h=0d16cbee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XhqaLeV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXhqaLeV.jpg&h=3a9235a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩完我地去咗實彈射擊場，嗰度有手槍，半自動同M4a1，價錢分別係前兩個3000菲 50發/m4 4000菲20發<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VG7AbRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVG7AbRN.jpg&h=885fd7c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNno5bL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNno5bL.jpg&h=28e3e93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DR5J5bP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDR5J5bP.jpg&h=75795def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0REDwR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0REDwR.jpg&h=a706432a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fU2gFLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfU2gFLe.jpg&h=87f0f62e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次玩槍覺得手槍同m4嘅後座力好正又夠響 ，係一次唔錯嘅體驗<br />\n<br />\n之後就叫司機車我地返去，食完晚飯就買酒返房飲。由於我要有三條友都因為疫情唔洗返工住，所以決定延長個行程，改機票5號返香港。另一個由於要返工，所以照原定返回"},{"pid":"fd260a2990ad7aed508009e96fa0601aae154c2a","tid":1849203,"uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪而家製劉菲律賓唔走得呀？"},{"pid":"9837efb7a4d20b417cb94c5f94304f8c40300d80","tid":1849203,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:47:28.000Z","msg":"If you ask me if Philippine is a decent holiday destination, I wouldn't bet on it. There's nothing worth doing there. The food is awful. I remember when I first tried Filipino food my nostrils flared in disgust. I wouldn't recommend visiting Philippine. One of the worst places on earth to go for your holiday."},{"pid":"626c4079b1a1ef38c04e77b69a393d8f1b23d7f7","tid":1849203,"uid":187891,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:56:56.000Z","msg":"希望樓主搭車果陣唔會俾人挾持啦"},{"pid":"84c446c434acf62b80f9db5c0eda73ce55e1a357","tid":1849203,"uid":16697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}